text: Vallée de l'Ernz () is a commune in Luxembourg. It is part of the canton of Diekirch. It was created on 1 January 2012 from the former communes of Ermsdorf and Medernach. As of 2019, 2,641 people live here. Category:2012 establishments in Luxembourg Category:Communes of Diekirch
title: Vallée de l'Ernz
